==Introduction==
零式艦上戦闘機の戦闘爆撃機仕様、通称「爆戦」の改良後期型です。改良型エンジンに換装、燃料タンクを防弾仕様化した零戦の性能向上型、53型。その胴体下に250kgまたは500kg爆弾懸吊架を増設、爆撃機動に耐えられるよう、一部機体強度も強化しています。重巡改装の攻撃型軽空母などで、ぜひ機動部隊運用を！

''An improved, late-model version of the Zero fighter-bomber. The improved Model 53 features an improved engine and bulletproof fuel tanks. Under the fuselage are added hardpoints for 250 or 500 kg bombs, and parts of the airframe have also been strengthened to better withstand the movements of bombing missions. Add it to the improved heavy cruisers and light carriers of your mobile task force!''

